vation-bidah","tag-misguidance-dallaal","tag-sunnah","tag-umar-ibn-al-khattab","tag-warning-al-nudhr"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9IV","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":28579,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/01\/ummah-ilm-fiqh-hadith\/","url_meta":{"origin":37381,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Ummah: Allah guides people of Fiqh, Hadith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah will not let my nation agree upon misguidance. The hand of Allah is over the united community.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \"The interpretation of the united community, according to the scholars, are the people of Fiqh,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11226,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/08\/institutes-good-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37381,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Guidance: Whoever institutes a good practice in Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Jarir reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever institutes a good practice in Islam will have its reward and the reward of whoever acts upon it without diminishing their rewards at all. Whoever institutes an evil practice in Islam will have its sin and the sin\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhaditho