llah sends astray, no one can guide him. The truest word\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":16,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/09\/08\/calling-righteousness-sin\/","url_meta":{"origin":37381,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Guidance: Whoever calls others to righteousness or sin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 8, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever calls to guidance will have a reward similar to those who follow him, without detracting from their rewards at all. Whoever calls to misguidance will have sin upon him similar to those who follow him, without\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19870,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/09\/19\/umar-on-secrecy\/","url_meta":{"origin":37381,"position":5},"title":"Umar on II Secrecy: Beware secret religious cults of misguidance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 19, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Awza\u2019i reported: Umar ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIf you see people meeting in secret for their religion to the exclusion of the public, then know that they are establishing misguidance.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 5\/388 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0632\u064e\u0627\u0639\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \